+1) export environment variables Geant4_DIR and ROOT_DIR. They must point to geant4/root cmake files (in case of valparaiso it is /opt/geant4/lib/Geant4-10.2.2 and /opt/root/cmake
+2) mkdir build; cd build
+3) cmake ../
+4) cmake --build . --config RelWithDebInfo  
+5) run

Another possibility is to use KDevelop. At the time of this push KDevelop 4.7 and 5 were tested and works.
